@node Main "Simonize - Documentation"

                             'Simonize'  1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Simonize' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} based on the old 'Simon' game,
where you try to repeat a sequence made by the computer. This game
displays a board containing a number of tiles, depending on the game
board size you want to play with (which you choose in the
@{" Main menu " link play}).

  When playing, the computer will highlight a number of tiles and
you have to click on the same tiles, in the same order. When you
imitate that sequence, the computer repeats it and highlight a new
tile and you must repeat the same sequence, and so on...

  'Simonize' can create a sequence of up to 250 tiles, will you be
able to repeat it?

  Have fun!

